Create a realistic 3D sculpture displayed in a modern art gallery. The sculpture should show a papaya cut in half, made of smooth white porcelain with a glazed finish. The inside of the papaya should be bright orange with many small black seeds filling the center. In the very middle, include a small area of gold leaf that reflects light slightly. Place the papaya on a white display pedestal. Around the papaya, arrange several white flower sculptures (cayeno flowers) with soft rounded petals and small red centers. The flowers should look delicate and organic. The lighting should feel like a museum setting, with soft overhead light creating gentle shadows underneath the sculpture. The background should be simple and neutral, like a gallery wall and floor, so the artwork stands out. Make the overall mood calm, slightly emotional, and meaningful. Focus on realistic texture, smooth porcelain surfaces, and subtle shine from the glaze and gold leaf.
